node.title: Auckland motorway closed southbound after multi-car crash
node.description: Police say the serious crash happened just after Gilles Ave.
node.content:
["A multi-car crash has closed the Auckland motorway southbound from GIlles Ave, Newmarket.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Police says the serious crash happened around 8.10pm.", "There are indications people have serious injuries, police said.", "Southbound lanes are closed from Newmarket and drivers will need to exit the motorway at Gillies Ave, getting back on at Greenlane."]
